Package: MAIHDA
Type: Package
Title: Multilevel Analysis of Individual Heterogeneity and Discriminatory Accuracy
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hamid", "Bulut", email = "hamid.bulut@uni.lu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides functions for conducting Multilevel Analysis of Individual
    Heterogeneity and Discriminatory Accuracy (MAIHDA). This package includes tools
    for creating strata, fitting multilevel models, summarizing results with variance
    partitioning, making predictions, and visualizing outcomes through various plot types.
